---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Beau Monde Salon Suites" description="Privacy policy for the Beau Monde Salon Suites website.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: March 4, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            This website itself does not directly collect personal information through cookies, account registrations, or analytics tracking. Like most websites, our hosting provider may automatically receive basic technical information (such as IP address and browser type) in server logs for security and operational purposes.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We do use a Google Form to collect contact information from prospective lessees interested in leasing a salon suite. Information submitted through that form may include your name, email address, phone number, and other details you choose to provide.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Information collected through Google Forms is stored and processed by Google in accordance with
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold transition-colors hover:text-gold-dark">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
            We use this information solely to respond to your inquiry and communicate with you about leasing opportunities. We do not sell your personal information.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We retain leasing inquiry information only as long as needed to respond and for our business records, unless a longer period is required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            This website does not use cookies or any similar tracking technologies. However, third-party websites we link to — including booking platforms, Google Forms, Instagram, and Facebook — may use their own cookies and tracking technologies. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those services before providing any information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Our site contains links to external websites and services, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Online booking platforms used by our professionals</li>
            <li>A Google Form for prospective lessee inquiries, which collects contact information you voluntarily submit</li>
            <li>Social media profiles on Instagram and Facebook</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            These third-party sites operate independently and have their own privacy policies. Salon professionals are independent businesses, and their booking platforms and privacy practices are their own. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these external sites. Any information you provide to those services is governed by their respective privacy policies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Professional Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            This site displays publicly available contact information for our salon professionals, such as email addresses and phone numbers, to help clients reach them directly. This information is provided by the professionals themselves and is not collected from visitors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Your Choices</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of the information you submitted by contacting us using the information below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Children</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            This site is not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
            <a href="tel:+19195518406" class="text-gold transition-colors hover:text-gold-dark">(919) 551-8406</a>
            or visit us at 300 S Main St, Holly Springs, NC 27540.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
